ABOUT LOGICA Logica is a UK owned international systems house with about 3000 employees in the UK and another 3000 in Holland, Germany, Italy, Australia, Hong Kong and elsewhere. In 1989 we acquired a US systems house called Data Architects to form Logica Data Architects which has about 850 employees with 10 offices in the US and 1 in Canada. Logica is an independent computer software, systems and consultancy company offering a source of expertise in advanced information technology to a range of market sectors including finance, communications, energy and industry, space and defence and other areas.